description:
Available at https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - As the pianist with the legendary bassist Ray Brown's trio from 1997-1999, Geoffrey had a front row seat every night to masterful walking bass lines. In this specially priced 3-video set, Geoffrey analyzes and demonstrates three excerpts which illustrate the melodic quality, variety, soulfulness, precision and flawless logic of Ray's bass lines. This information is highly valuable to any keyboard player interested in developing their left hand, and is great for anyone playing solo piano, organ, or accompanying vocalists. PDF included. 
(Level: Intermediate)
